Package: knitrmini
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Knitr Engine for Rnw -> TeX -> PDF
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal rewrite of knitr supporting rnoweb (.Rnw) to LaTeX
    to PDF conversion, with full knitr-compatible chunk options and caching.
    Produces clean LaTeX output without knitrout/kframe wrapping.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: evaluate (>= 0.15), highr (>= 0.11), xfun (>= 0.52), digest,
        tools, methods
Suggests: tinytex (>= 0.56)
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
Packaged: 2026-05-19 15:58:41 UTC; urtzi
